<br>
Also, keep in mind that by hitting &quot;shift&quot; and the number will switch you to a different bank of available slots.  You have 10 banks of 10 available, for 100 total slots.  Even in the &quot;windowed&quot; mode you can use all 10 slots once you have something in them, they just don't appear on the screen. <p>----------------------------<br>
